snippet.title: Air : game showing
snippet.description:
Fly a small paper plane!
Air is a game made to transport you to an enchanting world, forget your worries and let yourself be carried away by the atmosphere.
Available 30 October 2019 on Steam !

The link on Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1144520/Air/
Calepin Studio website : http://www.calepinstudio.com/index.php?page=air
Calepin Studio Twitter : https://twitter.com/CalepinStudio
Calepin Studio Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/CalepinStudio/
